      and optional solar-only charging when panels are producing.
    </p>

    <h3>Key Features</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Automatic pause when grid capacity is exceeded</li>
      <li>Solar-only charging mode (when PV is available)</li>
      <li>Full smartphone integration and remote control</li>
